{"title":"0. Fundamentos Ecografia-2026","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Neumología/0. Fundamentos Ecografia-2026.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"MÓDULO 0 —\\NFUNDAMENTOS TÉCNICOS\\NDE ECOGRAFÍA CLÍNICA","guid":"qhU7yYjMcUiOCg6iS4u3rQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"0.1 FÍSICA DEL\\NULTRASONIDO\\NAPLICADA","guid":"vnF3oHCuFAhQ86vTJJQD5w","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Onda sonora","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Frecuencia (Hz) → ciclos por segundo","guid":"jnpyoEs-lAZXC9HhJOO5eg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Longitud de onda (λ) → inversamente proporcional a frecuencia","guid":"zemqPTjHEdvjf-pmjr41Rg","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"Velocidad en tejido blando ~1540 m/s (asumida por equipo)","guid":"U3Ryfwkyiq1wzUQlIY-WoQ","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"2","text":"**A mayor frecuencia → mejor resolución axial, menor penetración**","guid":"7XY54DutYcOg3c2phOY7-w","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"2","text":"**A menor frecuencia → mayor penetración, menor resolución**","guid":"52EBmd3P6U2hJlIN0lVEtQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"Interacción onda-tejido","guid":"","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"Reflexión → interfases acústicas (base de la imagen)","guid":"WzOkyPTgPEjvyMXF-r2GBg","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"Refracción → cambio dirección al cruzar tejidos de diferente impedancia","guid":"ix4aef_9yYag_wUrmTO_vw","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"Atenuación → pérdida de\\Nenergía en profundidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Absorción (principal en tejido blando)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"Dispersión (scattering) → genera textura del parénquima","guid":"rFoGXeprZm7jzHYdpesqKA","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"8","text":"**Impedancia acústica** = densidad × velocidad → diferencia genera eco","guid":"CYlMY1mTcaM52GcACvIzPw","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"1","text":"Resolución","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Axial → capacidad de separar 2\\Npuntos en profundidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"Depende de frecuencia (↑ freq → ↑ resolución axial)","guid":"Ro2KSSEy6uQrRP5l6X7_Nw","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"~0.5-1 mm con transductor lineal alta frecuencia","guid":"wIkQCcBeGiB9KdE84lf2Tw","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"15","text":"Lateral → capacidad de\\Nseparar 2 puntos lado a lado","guid":"","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"Depende del ancho del haz → mejor en zona focal","guid":"fwqqdvEDaU7DbD-jjZYocQ","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"Siempre peor que axial","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"15","text":"Temporal → cuadros por\\Nsegundo (frame rate)","guid":"HAg-3J-FcXCj_vwxFDDIOw","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Importa en ecocardio → ↑ frame rate = mejor evaluación movimiento","guid":"jZYHZUNiG9LdFLDJrqSFMg","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"Trade-off: ↑ profundidad o ↑ sector → ↓ frame rate","guid":"2YM1PgEgA4c2v9oUoYE0ag","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"0.2 TRANSDUCTORES Y\\NSELECCIÓN POR CONTEXTO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"Convexo (curvilíneo)\\N2-5 MHz","guid":"G9o7wOS1lcUCdrkv4WKqMg","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"**Transductor más versátil**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Abdomen, FAST/eFAST, aorta, riñón, vesícula","guid":"ZN3EDe1GynzG97wfFO09xw","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"Eco pulmonar (si no hay lineal disponible)","guid":"Ox0TVn3tknKvrSVQwDsFog","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"VCI subcostal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"26","text":"Buena penetración, campo amplio en profundidad","guid":"5HNj6ySBd5GLJ8cHV1LdfA","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"25","text":"Lineal 6-15 MHz","guid":"","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"**Alta resolución superficial**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"Acceso vascular (CVC,\\Nvía periférica difícil)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"TVP (compresibilidad venosa)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"32","text":"Partes blandas (abscesos, celulitis)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"32","text":"Musculoesquelético\\N(sarcopenia → recto femoral)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"32","text":"Neumotórax (deslizamiento\\Npleural de alta definición)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"32","text":"Tiroides, vía aérea","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"25","text":"Sectorial (phased array) 1-5 MHz","guid":"","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"**Ecocardiografía focalizada**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"Huella pequeña →\\Ncabe entre costillas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"Ventanas: paraesternal,\\Napical, subcostal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"40","text":"Evaluación cardíaca y hemodinámica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"40","text":"Útil también para eco pulmonar","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"25","text":"Microconvexo 4-8 MHz","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Neonatal, pediátrico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Transcraneal (ventana temporal)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"Estructuras profundas en\\Nespacios reducidos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"25","text":"Selección rápida por escenario clínico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"Disnea aguda → sectorial (corazón) +\\Nlineal o convexo (pulmón)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"Shock → sectorial (RUSH bomba) +\\Nconvexo (RUSH tanque/tuberías)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"Acceso vascular → lineal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"50","text":"Dolor abdominal → convexo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"50","text":"TVP → lineal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"50","text":"Sarcopenia → lineal (recto femoral)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"0","text":"0.3 ORIENTACIÓN DEL\\NTRANSDUCTOR Y\\NCONVENCIONES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Marcador del transductor","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"Orientación estándar → marcador hacia\\N**cefálico** o **derecha del paciente**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"Pantalla → marcador corresponde al **punto\\Nverde/logo** en pantalla (izquierda)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"**Ecocardio → excepción**: marcador hacia\\Nderecha del paciente en apical","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"57","text":"Planos de corte","guid":"","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"Longitudinal (sagital) →\\Nmarcador cefálico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"Transversal (axial) → marcador\\Na derecha del paciente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"62","text":"Coronal → marcador cefálico (ej:\\NMorrison, esplenorrenal)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"57","text":"Movimientos del transductor","guid":"","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"Deslizar (sliding) →\\Ntraslación sobre la piel","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"Inclinar (tilting) → angular sin\\Nmover punto de contacto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"66","text":"Rotar (rotating) → girar sobre su eje","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"66","text":"Presionar (compression) →\\Nacercar estructuras profundas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"66","text":"Abanico (fanning) → barrido angular","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"57","text":"Documentación estandarizada","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Etiquetado: iniciales paciente,\\Nfecha, plano, indicación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Clips >3 seg en cardíaco\\N(mínimo 2-3 ciclos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"Imágenes estáticas con\\Nmediciones congeladas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"Registro en ficha clínica →\\Nhallazgo + implicancia clínica","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"0","text":"0.4 OPTIMIZACIÓN DE IMAGEN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"Controles principales (KNOBOLOGÍA)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"**Ganancia** (gain)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"General → brillo global de la imagen","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"TGC (time gain compensation) →\\Ncompensar atenuación por profundidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"Regla: si imagen muy brillante → ↓\\Nganancia; si oscura → ↑ ganancia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"78","text":"**Profundidad** (depth)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Ajustar para que estructura de\\Ninterés ocupe ~2/3 de pantalla","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"↑ profundidad → ↓ frame rate","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"Error común: profundidad excesiva →\\Nestructuras pequeñas e irreconocibles","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"78","text":"**Foco** (focus)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"Ubicar a nivel de\\Nestructura de interés","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"Mejor resolución lateral en zona focal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"78","text":"**Frecuencia** (si ajustable)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"↑ para estructuras superficiales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"↓ para mayor penetración","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"78","text":"**Zoom**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"Usar post-adquisición\\Npara mediciones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"Zoom pre-adquisición mejora\\Nresolución pero reduce campo","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"77","text":"Modos ecográficos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Modo B (brillantez) → imagen 2D\\Nestándar, base de todo POCUS","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"Modo M (movimiento) → evalúa\\Nmovimiento en el tiempo sobre una línea","guid":"","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"Aplicaciones: deslizamiento pleural\\N(seashore sign), excursión diafragmática,\\NTAPSE, movimiento valvular","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"96","text":"Doppler color → flujo\\Nsuperpuesto en imagen 2D","guid":"","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"Rojo = flujo hacia el transductor\\N(BART: Blue Away Red Toward)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"Azul = flujo alejándose\\Ndel transductor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"Aliasing → velocidad excede límite\\NNyquist → turbulencia aparente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"104","parent":"96","text":"Doppler pulsado (PW) → mide\\Nvelocidad en punto específico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"VTI en TSVI → cálculo\\Nde gasto cardíaco","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"104","text":"E/A mitral, e' tisular →\\Npresiones de llenado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"104","text":"**Ángulo de insonación <60°\\Nobligatorio** → error ↑ con ángulo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"96","text":"Doppler continuo (CW) → mide\\Nvelocidades altas sin límite","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Jet de insuficiencia\\Ntricuspídea → estimar PAPs","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"Gradiente aórtico en estenosis","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"77","text":"Paciente difícil →\\Noptimización específica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"**Obeso**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"Transductor de menor\\Nfrecuencia (convexo 2-3 MHz)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"↑ ganancia, ↓ frecuencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"Ventana subcostal a veces\\Nmejor que paraesternal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"Armónicos tisulares (tissue harmonic\\Nimaging) → mejora contraste","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"111","text":"**Enfisematoso/EPOC**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"Hiperinsuflación → ventanas\\Nintercostales estrechas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"Sectorial > convexo para cardíaco","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"Ventana subcostal\\Nfrecuentemente la mejor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"117","text":"Sentar al paciente e\\Nintentar ventana apical","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"111","text":"**Ventilado en UCI**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"Decúbito supino obligado →\\Ndificulta ventana apical","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"PEEP alta → ↓ retorno venoso\\N→ VCI menos confiable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"Eco pulmonar en 6-8 zonas\\N(protocolo BLUE adaptado)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"122","text":"Considerar transesofágico si\\Nventanas muy malas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"111","text":"**Heridas/apósitos**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"Cubrir transductor con funda estéril","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"Gel estéril","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"127","text":"Ventanas alternativas\\Nalejadas del sitio quirúrgico","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"0","text":"0.5 ARTEFACTOS\\NECOGRÁFICOS ÚTILES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Sombra acústica posterior","guid":"","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"Estructura hiperecogénica bloquea\\Nhaz → sombra negra detrás","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"**Útil**: cálculos biliares, cálculos\\Nrenales, calcificaciones","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"131","text":"Refuerzo acústico posterior","guid":"","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"Estructura anecoica (líquido) → menos\\Natenuación → brillo posterior","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"**Útil**: confirmar naturaleza\\Nquística, derrame, vejiga llena","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"131","text":"Reverberación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"Reflexiones múltiples entre\\Ninterfases paralelas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"Líneas A en pulmón normal →\\Nreverberación de pleura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"138","text":"**Líneas A = pulmón aireado** (normal o\\Nneumotórax según contexto)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"131","text":"Cola de cometa / Líneas B","guid":"","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"Reverberación de alta frecuencia\\Nen interfases pequeñas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"**Líneas B** → artefactos verticales desde\\Npleura hasta fondo de pantalla","guid":"","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"Aisladas (≤2 por campo) = normal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"**≥3 por campo = edema\\Nintersticial / congestión**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"Confluentes = edema alveolar franco","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"142","text":"Diferencial: cardiogénico vs\\NSDRA vs neumonitis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"131","text":"Imagen en espejo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"Reflexión en superficie\\Ncurva (diafragma)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"Hígado \"aparece\" sobre diafragma → NO\\Nconfundir con consolidación","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"131","text":"Artefacto de anisotropía","guid":"","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"Tendones/nervios cambian\\Necogenicidad según ángulo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"Relevante en eco MSK y\\Nbloqueos nerviosos","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas ⭐","guid":"","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"**Antes de tocar al paciente**: seleccionar\\Ntransductor + preset + profundidad → ahorra\\Ntiempo en urgencia/UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"**Ganancia y profundidad son los\\N2 ajustes más impactantes** →\\Ndominarlos primero","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"155","text":"El **modo M** es subutilizado →\\Nimprescindible para neumotórax\\N(barcode vs seashore) y TAPSE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"155","text":"**Líneas B ≥3 bilateral = congestión\\Nhasta demostrar lo contrario** →\\Nintegrar con clínica y VCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"155","text":"En el **anciano obeso en UCI**:\\Narmónicos tisulares + subcostal +\\Nsectorial = combinación ganadora","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"155","text":"**Ángulo de insonación <60°** →\\Nerror del Doppler crece\\Nexponencialmente sobre 60°","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"155","text":"**BART** (Blue Away, Red Toward) →\\Nmnemotecnia para Doppler color","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"155","text":"El artefacto de **imagen en espejo** sobre\\Ndiafragma es la causa más frecuente de falso\\Npositivo de derrame pleural en principiantes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"155","text":"**Documentar SIEMPRE**: imagen\\Nsin medición ni interpretación\\Nregistrada = examen no hecho","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"155","text":"Para el geriatra: la eco en **ADG con transductor\\Núnico** (convexo) permite evaluar vejiga,\\Nhidronefrosis, derrame pleural y VCI → alto\\Nrendimiento con mínimo equipo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"0","text":"VER TAMBIEN\\n(mapas relacionados)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"-> Derrame pleural\\n[Neumología]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"-> Ecocardio\\n[Cardiología]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"175","text":"-> Tiroides\\n[Endocrinología]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"175","text":"-> PROFUND\\n[UCI-Medicina Crítica]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"175","text":"-> REDUCE\\n[General]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"175","text":"-> FOCUS\\n[General]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"175","text":"-> Trans\\n[General]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"175","text":"-> Dolor\\n[root]","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":183,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Neumología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neumología","filename":"0. Fundamentos Ecografia-2026","id":"map_1341","resolved_references":[]}